        "timestamp": "2020-01-15 10:22:39.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> Patch Set 1: Code-Review+1\n> \n> Do we run this scenario in ci/cd or just manually?\n\nI'm sorry but I unintentionally lied to you in previous comment: molecule doesn't run all scenarios by default, it runs only \"default\". \n\nWe test all scenarios by explicit cmd line arguments to molecule:\n\nansible/test/bin/ci-molecule.sh\n52  ${MOLECULE_BINARY} test --all\n\nSo my answer to your question still holds true, it's just the reasoning that changes.",
